  <description>Library to manage NDF QUALITY information textually
  </description>
  <abstract><p> 
     This library is a set of Fortran routines that provides looping of 
     tasks within a monolith, in order to allow a command to be invoked 
     repeatedly until all supplied data files (catalogues or NDFs) have 
     been processed.  Thus it can be used to enable lists of files
     including wildcards to be processed in a single command.
  </p></abstract>
